Introduction

Kim Hyunwoo, better known as Baekseung, is a South Korean rapper of the boy group EPEX under C9 Entertainment. Before making his official debut in 2021, Baekseung first appeared in the survival program "CAP-TEEN" as a trainee.

In 2021 Baekseung acted in the drama "Hometown Cha-Cha-Cha" where he appeared in a couple of episodes playing the role of a famous 'first love' idol member.
